decks.notes: This deck focuses on aggressive gameplay with the use of the Partner commanders Bruse Tarl and Yoshimaru. The strategy involves quickly building up a board presence with efficient creatures like Thalia, Guardian of Thraben and Isamaru, Hound of Konda. Removal spells like Swords to Plowshares and Lightning Bolt help control the opponent's threats while keeping up the pressure. The deck also includes powerful equipments such as Embercleave and Skullclamp to enhance the effectiveness of the creatures. The mana base is optimized for quick access to the necessary colors and includes utility lands like Eiganjo Castle and Sunbaked Canyon. Overall, the deck aims to overwhelm the opponent with a fast and aggressive game plan.
